rComments: He's way to smart to convey tax material to his students.  If you don't pay attention, you will have a tough time because he's already hard to understand. HIGHLY suggest taking notes/bullet points about topics he talks about because his tests are all conceptual.  Overall, hard class, hard teacher, workload isn't bad/fair.
Really cool professor, and teaches the material pretty well. Reassured my decision to go into tax accounting and was always available to help or answer questions.
